.Dd February 7, 2025
.Dt DEVFDT 4D
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm devfdt
.Nd read-only access to the system flat device tree
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Pa /dev/fdt
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Nm
driver provides
.Pa /dev/fdt
a character device which exposes the flat device tree blob (dtb) used by this
system to userland.
Utilities such as
.Xr dtc 1
can be used to inspect this data.
.Sh INTERFACE STABILITY
Volatile
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr dtc 1 ,
.Xr fdt 5
.Sh NOTES
Only enough features to support tools such as
.Xr dtc 1
exist, notably there is no support for
.Xr mmap 2 .
